      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Talking Darfur to Death'' (editorial, March 31):</p>
        <p>It's pathetic and illuminating that if Darfur had oil, we'd be dashing to stop the genocide -- absolutely pathetic!</p>
        <p>Thom Stayart  Dallas, March 31, 2007</p>
